NUMBER 3600
  NAME The Foyer
  *DESCRIPTION_START
This is a tastefully appointed, well maintained, extremely proper entrance hall. It looks like the sort of thing you would find in an explorer's club, and very little like a resort. Red carpeting covers the floor, leading from the door into the main room, which lies to the north. Five portraits line the walls, two on the left, and three on the right.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  INDOOR_FLOOR
  FIXED_LIGHT
  EXIT N 3601
  ITEM 0 943  ADJ1=216  VAL1=5000  VAL2=266  VAL3=3666
  ITEM 1 1308
  ITEM 2 1308
  ITEM 3 1308
  ITEM 4 1308
  ITEM 5 1308
  EXTEND 1 of Parvenu Rocmartin
  EXTEND 2 of Notable the Cat
  EXTEND 3 of Schrodingerscat Meow
  EXTEND 4 of Billy Whitman
  EXTEND 5 of Brook Hoaquin
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
You see Parvenu Rocmartin, a silver-colored woman in white with an odd mohawked hairdo. She seems to be leaning on a halberd.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
You see Notable, a large red cat. He looks impishly mischevious, and you'd almost swear you can hear him purr.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
You see Schrodingerscat Meow. Or do you? It's hard to tell if he's dead or alive, or even if he's there at all.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
You see a picture of Billy Whitman, a small boy. He bears an uncanny resemblance to Armoth Whitman, one of the Resort's founders.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
You see a picture of Brook Hoaquin, an oddly-dressed man with a benevolent expression on his face. He seems overly fond of his quarterstaff, which he is leaning on for support.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
NUMBER 3601
  NAME The Sitting Room
  *DESCRIPTION_START
This is a comfortable, lived in room. Two couches rest here, and three portraits hang on the walls. A large scratching post stands in one corner, with a few toys scattered around it. Nearby, you can see two large plastic bowls, bearing the names 'Notable' and 'Loup'. An ashtray rests on an endtable between the couches, whose ashes give off an odd odor which causes your head to spin.
On one wall hangs a large captain's wheel, next to which stands a perch, on which rests a colorful parrot. To the south is the entrance hall, and to the west you can see another large room. A stairway leads up to the second story.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  INDOOR_FLOOR
  FIXED_LIGHT
  EXIT S 3600
  EXIT W 3602
  ITEM 0 1308
  ITEM 1 1308
  ITEM 2 1308
  ITEM 3 1076
  ITEM 4 448  ADJ1=587
  ITEM 5 448  ADJ1=587
  ITEM 6 1594
  ITEM 7 1024  ADJ1=178  ADJ2=355
  ITEM 8 1077  ADJ1=425
  ITEM 9 81  VAL2=3603
  EXTEND 0 of Rasta Farian
  EXTEND 1 of Armoth Whitman
  EXTEND 2 of Loup Gamin
  EXTEND 3 covered with carpeting
  EXTEND 4 with the word 'Loup' written on it
  EXTEND 5 with the word 'Notable' written on it
  EXTEND 6 whose ashes smell funny and make your head spin
  EXTEND 7 with many spokes which extend past the rim
  PUT 4 1410  ADJ1=499  ADJ2=162
  PUT 5 1410  ADJ1=499  ADJ2=162
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
Rasta Farian has a dazed, sleepy look on his face. His skin is dark, his clothing is colorful, and his hair is in dreadlocks. He has a halo of gray smoke around his head.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
Armoth is short, with dark hair, dressed in a flowing white shirt he wove himself. He is wearing a bandanna on his head, and has a parrot resting on one shoulder.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
This is a picture of a wolf, sitting on its haunches. It has gray eyes, and dark brown fur, and seems to be wagging its tail.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
This is a tall wooden post, wrapped in carpet. It is covered with many large scratch marks, and the carpet is just about falling off in places.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  OPEN 4
  OPEN 5
  IFPREVERB SNIFF 6
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You sniff an ashtray.
    ECHO OTHERS %N sniffs an ashtray and looks dizzy.
    ECHO PLAYER The room seems to spin around you, dancing this way and that as many interesting colors fill your vision.
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB LOOK 8
    ECHO ALL A colorful parrot squawks, "Polly want a cracker!"
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB PET 8
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You pet a colorful parrot.
    ECHO OTHERS %N pets a colorful parrot.
    ECHO ALL It lowers its head so you can get at just the right spot on the back of its neck.
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB PUSH 3
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You rub up against a scratching post.
    ECHO OTHERS %N rubs %h back up against a scratching post.
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB PULL 3
    IFVAR SKILL4 > 0
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You sharpen your claws on a scratching post.
      ECHO OTHERS %N sharpens %h claws on a scratching post.
      IFVAR SKILL4 > 5
        SPELL 534 30
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB THUMP 8
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You thump %a.
    ECHO OTHERS %N thumps %a!
    IFVAR EXITD = 3612
      ECHO ALL It leaps up with a startled SQUAWK! and flutters this way and that around the room. It swoops down past your head, closing the trapdoor into the basement, and finally settles down on its perch.
      EQUAL EXITD 0
    ENDIF
    IFVAR EXITD = -1
      ECHO ALL With a SQUAWK! it leaps of its perch and flutters around the room. It swoops down past your head, and dives for a ring in the floor, which it pulls, revealing a hidden opening. It then settles back down on its perch.
      EQUAL EXITD 3612
    ENDIF
    IFVAR EXITD = 0
      EQUAL EXITD -1
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
NUMBER 3602
  NAME The Ballroom
  *DESCRIPTION_START
This is a huge, open room with a polished wooden floor. A crystal chandelier hangs from the ceiling. Two portraits hang on the walls, and a large grand piano with a silver candleabra upon it stands in the corner. To the east, you can just make out the sitting room.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  INDOOR_FLOOR
  FIXED_LIGHT
  EXIT E 3601
  ITEM 0 1308
  ITEM 1 1308
  ITEM 2 1966  ADJ1=163  ADJ2=25
  EXTEND 0 of Nadia Cedenya
  EXTEND 1 of Dementus Chikan
  EXTEND 2 with a silver candleabra upon it
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
Nadia is a voluptuous woman who isn't wearing much. Her image gazes at you with a smoldering passion which causes something within you to stir.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  *DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
Dementus Chikan is a rather unassuming looking man. He is wearing an extremely colorful cloak over an even more colorful tunic, and is holding a violin in one hand.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  IFPREVERB GO 2
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You climb up on top of the piano.
    ECHO OTHERS %N climbs up on top of the piano.
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB TICKLE 2
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You lightly tap out a melody on the keys of the piano.
    ECHO OTHERS %N plays a light, springy tune, causing your feet to start tapping and your fingers to start snapping.
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB THUMP 2
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You bang on the keys, producing a loud dramatic chord.
    ECHO OTHERS %N plays a loud, dramatic chord on the piano.
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB PUSH 2
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You play a tune on the piano.
    ECHO OTHERS %N plays a lovely tune on the piano.
  ENDIF
