*DESCRIPTION_START
Suits of armor from every culture skirt the hallway as it leads deeper into the mansion. Paintings on the walls show the images of various unknown, rakish individuals. The sound of revelry is more intense, but you can't tell quite where it is coming from.
*DESCRIPTION_END
