Candelabras along the walls contain burning candles that flicker eerily across this combination sitting room and library. A soft leather chair sits by a book shelf containing numerous volumes of text as well as the odd scroll or stone tablet. The sound of revelry is even more intense here, but you still can't tell quite where it is coming from.
*DESCRIPTION_END
