    ENDIF
    IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = 2
      EQUAL ITEMVAL5 1
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB LOOK 6
    CLEARVERB
    IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = 0
      ECHO PLAYER The portrait depicts a short woman with long, black hair. Walking barefoot through the forest clad in a beautiful robe, she smiles softly as she sings to a young girl, as beautiful as a princess, walking beside her.
    ENDIF
    IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = 1
      ECHO PLAYER The portrait depicts a tall dark-skinned woman with long coarse black hair. Clad in various shades of blue, she smiles as the winds swirl around her. One hand upraised to the sky, she seems in total control of the elements.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
